name: You Would Do It Too
overview: A bus is hijacked by three robbers—who end up dead before they can get away. Every passenger's story is the same: A hooded man saved the day. As the case unfolds, the line between hero and criminal begins to blur.

episodes.name: Three Dead on a Bus
episodes.overview: A mysterious man flees after taking down three criminals robbing the bus he's on. Police question the passengers, who claim to know nothing.

episodes.name: Pact of Silence
episodes.overview: Detectives Garza and Quirós suspect the passengers are hiding the truth. Meanwhile, social media celebrates the hooded man as a hero.

episodes.name: The Justice
episodes.overview: Garza and Quirós finally get a lead as a tenacious television reporter begins looking into the bus vigilante dubbed “El Justiciero.”
